folder: Sterling Place & Flatbush Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
160-184 Sterling Place, south side, west from Flatbush to Seventh Aves., showing also at the right foreground, the N.W. corner of Flatbush Ave. and Sterling Place. In the background next to No. 160, is a new Christian Science Church.*

January 1, 1937.

P. L. Sperr.

* Fourth Church of Christ, Scientist. 156 Sterling Place.
